"""ribosome-review — META-RIBOSOME: reviews other ribosome output, diagnoses failures, queues more work.

Reads ribosome-daemon.log to find completed tasks, validates output files,
runs tests on new test files, checks consulting content quality, diagnoses
common failure patterns, and auto-generates new tasks when the queue is low.

Usage:
    ribosome-review [--auto-requeue] [--since 30m] [--once]
    ribosome-review --help
"""

